---
<section id="contact">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="contact-inner fade-in">
      <p class="section-label">What's Next</p>
      <h2>Let's talk.</h2>
      <p class="contact-sub">
        I'm open to roles in defense, aerospace, AI, and fintech — particularly where finance meets automation. I'm also always happy to talk shop on trading systems, valuation models, or building SaaS from zero.
      </p>
      <a href="mailto:robertdegon14@gmail.com" class="contact-btn">
        Send me a message →
      </a>
      <div class="contact-socials">
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/robdegonda" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn ↗</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/robdegonda" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub ↗</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #contact {
    padding-bottom: 120px;
  }

  .contact-inner {
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  #contact h2 { margin-bottom: 20px; }

  .contact-sub {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .contact-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--bg);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 16px;
    padding: 14px 32px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .contact-btn:hover { opacity: 0.85; transform: translateY(-1px); text-decoration: none; }

  .contact-socials {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .contact-socials a {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .contact-socials a:hover { color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; }
</style>
